<p style="text-align: center;">今年11月9日</p><p style="text-align: center;">是第33个全国消防日</p><p style="text-align: center;">国务院安委会办公室定于11月份</p><p style="text-align: center;">在全国开展消防宣传月活动</p><p style="text-align: center;">活动主题为</p><p style="text-align: center;">全民消防、生命至上</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241108/1731040207122063798.jpg" title="1731040207122063798.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241108113922.jpg" width="712" height="1457" style="width: 712px; height: 1457px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241108/1731040257090089508.jpg" title="1731040257090089508.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241108113930.jpg" width="705" height="1493" style="width: 705px; height: 1493px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241108/1731040305348053950.jpg" title="1731040305348053950.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241108113937.jpg" width="699" height="1530" style="width: 699px; height: 1530px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241108/1731040355301025591.jpg" title="1731040355301025591.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241108113944.jpg" width="697" height="1503" style="width: 697px; height: 1503px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241108/1731040410854015557.jpg" title="1731040410854015557.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241108114028.jpg" width="700" height="1562" style="width: 700px; height: 1562px;"/></p>